## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped — GH#440 standalone distribution

1. **Version management** — `internal/version/version.go` with build-time ldflags injection (Version, Commit, Date). Banner and /settings about use dynamic version.

2. **.gitignore** — standard Go ignores plus binary output.

3. **GitHub Actions CI** — `.github/workflows/ci.yml`. Runs on push/PR. Checks out both skrptiq-cli and skrptiq-app repos side by side. Builds, tests, vets. Requires `ENGINE_ACCESS_TOKEN` secret.

4. **GitHub Actions Release** — `.github/workflows/release.yml`. Triggered on tag push `v*`. Builds 5 platform binaries (darwin arm64/amd64, linux amd64/arm64, windows amd64) with CGO on native runners. Generates SHA256 checksums. Creates GitHub Release with all artifacts.

5. **curl installer** — `scripts/install.sh`. Detects OS/arch, downloads correct binary from GitHub Releases, verifies SHA256, installs to ~/.local/bin/skrptiq. Supports SKRPTIQ_VERSION and SKRPTIQ_INSTALL_DIR env vars.

